import React from 'react'
import About from './About'
import Contact from './Contact'
import Error from './Error'
import { Routes, Route } from 'react-router-dom'

const App = () => {
  return (
    <>

      <Routes>
        <Route p />
      </Routes>

      <About />
      <Contact/>
      <Error/>
    </>
  )
}

export default App
